Deg ussan-nni, a d-yas m'ara d-uɣaleɣ a ten-id-yaweḍ wedrum agi n imawlan-nsen, anagar tamurt-nni i d-yusan si tmurt n Yahuda akk-d leǧwahi yellan di tmurt n Tqenṭert, si tmurt n Asya, wiyaḍ ț-țmurt n nnger.
